rules: Rule1: Whenever compound A is identified, compound A is extracted.
Rule2: Either compound A is purified or compound A is not extracted.
Rule3: Financial product F is stored or vehicle V is not delivered.

Rule4: Under the condition that financial product F is analyzed, if it is not the case that trading financial product F implies financial product F is not stored, then financial product F is regulated.
Rule5: Supposing that financial product F is invested, then financial product F is profitable or drug X is profitable.
Rule6: In the event that financial product F is funded, either financial product F is profitable or drug X is profitable.
Rule7: If drug X is developed, then financial product F is invested or financial product F is funded.
Rule8: Drug X is patented or drug X is developed.
Rule9: Drug X is produced or drug X is manufactured.
Rule10: If compound A is safe, then should drug X not be profitable, drug X is not approved.
Rule11: When compound A is manufactured, compound A is approved.
Rule12: In the event that compound A is produced, then if compound A is tested, compound A is safe.
Rule13: Either compound A is recalled or, under the condition that it is not the case that compound A is manufactured or produced, compound A is banned.
Rule14: Whenever compound A is warned, compound A is restricted.
Rule15: If compound A is restricted, then compound A is controlled.
Rule16: When compound A is monitored, then if compound A is controlled, compound A is not toxic.
Rule17: Assuming drug X is manufactured, either drug X is tested or, should drug X not be profitable, drug X is not approved.
Rule18: If compound A is supervised, then provided that compound A is controlled, compound A is not toxic.
Rule19: Whenever compound A is inspected, compound A is monitored.
Rule20: Either compound A is inspected or compound A is audited.
Rule21: In the event that compound A is verified, then if compound A is audited, compound A is supervised.
Rule22: Compound A is verified or compound A is certified.
Rule23: If compound A is certified, then whenever compound A is audited, compound A is supervised.
Rule24: Either drug X is marketed or drug X is developed.
Rule25: Provided that drug X is promoted, then either drug X is advertised or drug X is not marketed.
Rule26: Either drug X is promoted or drug X is endorsed.
Rule27: Under the condition that drug X is endorsed, either drug X is advertised or drug X is not marketed.
Rule28: Either drug X is distributed or drug X is supplied.
Rule29: Supposing that drug X is supplied, then if drug X is produced, either drug X is tested or, under the condition that drug X is not profitable, drug X is not approved.
Rule30: When drug X is prescribed, then if drug X is distributed, then provided that drug X is produced, either drug X is tested or, should drug X not be profitable, drug X is not approved.
Rule31: If disease Y is researched, then study Z is published.
Rule32: Provided that it is not the case that compound A is manufactured or produced, compound A is not banned.
Rule33: In the event that it is not the case that publishing study Z implies drug X is profitable, compound A is identified.

Rule34: If it is not the case that the negation of the negation of the negation of the negation of the negation of the statement "if drug X is not profitable, then plant P is derived" implies plant P is not cultivated implies compound A is not toxic implies compound A is safe, then compound A is approved.

Rule35: Under the condition that it is not the case that the negation of the negation of the negation of the negation of the negation of the statement "if drug X is not profitable, then plant P is derived" implies plant P is not cultivated implies compound A is not toxic implies compound A is safe, then compound A is not approved.

Rule36: Supposing that it is not the case that the negation of the negation of the negation of the negation of the statement "if drug X is not profitable, then plant P is derived" implies plant P is not cultivated implies compound A is not toxic, then compound A is not safe.

Rule37: In the event that it is not the case that the negation of the negation of the negation of the statement "if drug X is not profitable, then plant P is derived" implies plant P is not cultivated, then compound A is toxic.

Rule38: Provided that it is not the case that the negation of the negation of the negation of the statement "if drug X is not profitable, then plant P is derived" implies plant P is not cultivated, then compound A is warned.
Rule39: If it is not the case that the negation of the negation of the statement "if drug X is not profitable, then plant P is derived", then plant P is cultivated.
Rule40: Supposing that it is not the case that the negation of the negation of the statement "if drug X is not profitable, then vehicle V is processed", then vehicle V is delivered.
Rule41: Whenever drug X is not profitable, drug X is approved.

Fact2: Financial product F is analyzed.
Fact6: Compound A is not purified.
Fact7: Plant P is not derived.
Fact8: Vehicle V is not processed.

Fact10: It is not the case that financial product F is regulated.

Fact15: Drug X is not advertised.
